Ku Chan Seong?

272
00:17:01,884 --> 00:17:04,185
Dia bukan lagi pengurus besar kita.

273
00:17:04,210 --> 00:17:05,939
Saya tahu ia juga mengganggu awak.

274
00:17:05,964 --> 00:17:07,784
Mari kahwinkan dia
dengan keluarga kaya itu.

275
00:17:07,809 --> 00:17:09,449
