304
00:18:53,812 --> 00:18:54,983
Awak suka kasut coklat murah...

305
00:18:55,951 --> 00:18:58,751
Maksud saya, awak suka
warna biasa seperti coklat.

306
00:18:59,291 --> 00:19:00,396
Bukan?

307
00:19:00,421 --> 00:19:02,169
