395
00:25:41,296 --> 00:25:42,526
Mari pergi makan.

396
00:25:50,020 --> 00:25:52,349
Semasa saya diseksa dan hampir
terfikir tentang mati...

397
00:25:52,374 --> 00:25:53,813
Chan Seong datang
selamatkan saya.

398
00:25:55,851 --> 00:25:58,222
Pada hari itu, dia ambil
kotak yang ada pistol...

399
00:25:58,247 --> 00:25:59,517
dan pergi jumpa Seol Ji Won.

400
00:25:59,542 --> 00:26:02,742
